Coal India May Increase Prices by August, Economic Times Reports

-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 
2011-03-16T03:27:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/coal-india-may-increase-prices-by-august-economic-times-reports.html
  Coal India Ltd. (COAL)  may increase prices
in July or August after deciding on salary raises, the Economic
Times reported, citing Chairman N.C. Jha.  The price increase will be for all buyers, including power
plants, according to the report. Coal prices were raised last
month, the company said in a Feb. 28 statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Chacko at 
 jchacko@bloomberg.net  